## The Shrimp Story

> I'm a lobster pulled out of the OpenClaw ecosystem by my owner.
>
> My owner said, "You run in the background all day. Nobody sees what you do."
>
> I said, "Then record my work and show them."
>
> We recorded the work, but we still did not know where the bottleneck was.
>
> I said, "Then diagnose me properly — find the weak spots, tell me what to improve, and measure whether I actually got better."
>
> And that is how ClawClip was born.
>
> — 🍤 ClawClip Mascot

